<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شِقَاقٍ بَعِيدٍ}</span> ... مُنَازَعَةٍ، وَخِلافٍ بَعِيدٍ عَنِ الحَقِّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
